{"tid":2490271,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「近千名人才加入無綫」網民：黃尸又眼紅！！","createTime":"2021-04-15T12:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T13:05:41.000Z","uid":219635,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c83f6d2c7692c421c7a1ba717f956e39bdf2b061","tid":2490271,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:50:47.000Z","msg":"自曾志偉上任TVB高層後，接連推出多個節目，在坊間引起不少話題。今日TVB在電視城舉行《2021藝員及電視製作人員訓練班面試》，現場約有700人參加面試，應徵當幕後人員，副總經理曾志偉適逢今日生日，在場向面試者分享入行感受。<br />\n<br />\n今日TVB舉行《2021藝員及電視製作人員訓練班面試》，早前公布共有逾2千人提交報名表，今日在電視城先進行幕後工作人員面試，約有700人出席，坐滿錄影廠，而下星期則會舉行藝員面試。 <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">入行最佳時機！</span><br />\n曾志偉又指現在是入行最好的時間，因現在是電視的里程碑。志偉並稱:「打這份工不止滿足自己興趣，還要兼顧社會責任，將社會資訊、娛樂、傳遞給大家。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2931850/【兩台大戰】TVB辦招聘會700人迫爆廠%E3%80%80曾志偉招兵買馬：係電視里程碑\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2931850%2F%E3%80%90%E5%85%A9%E5%8F%B0%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%B0%E3%80%91TVB%E8%BE%A6%E6%8B%9B%E8%81%98%E6%9C%83700%E4%BA%BA%E8%BF%AB%E7%88%86%E5%BB%A0%25E3%2580%2580%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89%E6%8B%9B%E5%85%B5%E8%B2%B7%E9%A6%AC%EF%BC%9A%E4%BF%82%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E9%87%8C%E7%A8%8B%E7%A2%91&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwLvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=8a78e44f\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2931850/【兩台大戰】TVB辦招聘會700人迫爆廠%E3%80%80曾志偉招兵買馬：係電視里程碑</a>"},{"pid":"ef93e7b848301596373dc059abdda45d7a49ebee","tid":2490271,"uid":219635,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:52:20.000Z","msg":"支持追夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢哋都係為生活，無得簡，係暗黃係手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連仔全力支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20b4e02f5d93c91aff90d3cbf025b5ceb